Class Model_Invoice

  • java.lang.Object
    • Data.Model_Invoice

  • public class Model_Invoice
extends Object
    The main invoice Fields: id_invoice - ID of this specific invoice id_user - ID of the user tied to this invoice totalPrice - price of all items tied to this invoice (Model) Model_invoiceDetails - The InvoiceDetails (order details) related to this specific invoice (ArrayList) invoiceDetails a complete list of all related InvoiceDetails
